Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

Your case is located at our Potomac Service Center location. Please follow any instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your duplicate notice by July 24, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request a copy of the notice.
